    "7280": "images.autodesk.com/adsk/files/tips_for_optimizing_your_model0.pdf",
    "7281": "Project Settings are stored in the Autodesk project and take precedence over My Settings and Classic AutoCAD Settings. Project administration access is required to modify.",
